      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下FinTech支付系统的核心流程，从PaymentGateway开始，经过TransactionQueue，最后到LedgerService。能不能先画一个主干流程？",
      "elements_involved": [
