    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，主干是从PaymentGateway发起，经过队列处理，最终落账到LedgerService。我先把这个骨架搭起来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
